data.description: Welcome to your Paradise retreat in Paradise Estates! This beautiful home is located on the south side of Woodland Park giving you easy access to Colorado Springs avoiding the drive through downtown woodland park. This home is a mountain getaway but only minutes away from all the necessities. You will love the large deck to enjoy the stunning views of Pikes Peak. The Master Bedroom is amazing on its own level with a private 5 piece bathroom and 2 walkout balconies that have amazing views. The basement is set up as its own private living area with a full kitchen that would be great for Airbnb. This is such an amazing opportunity in Woodland Park.
